OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FJamie Oliver: Sugar tax    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcould fund school meals    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Jamie Oliver has said the millions     
OL,6, being raised through the so-called     
OL,7, sugar tax should be used to extend the 
OL,8, provision of free school meals.        
OL,10,FThe chef and food campaigner wants at  
OL,11,Fleast 800,000 more children to benefit.
OL,13,FHe was instrumental in persuading the  
OL,14,Fgovernment in 2018 to impose the levy  
OL,15,Fon soft drinks with high sugar content.
OL,17,FInitially the funds raised were used   
OL,18,Ffor programmes to tackle childhood     
OL,19,Fobesity but now Oliver wants them to be
OL,20,Fdiverted to the school meals programme.
